timelineItems.name: Inside MLS
timelineItems.text: Philadelphia and Montréal just kicked off at a rainy PPL Park. Decent chance for Impact to pick up rare road win. #PHIvMTL #MLS

timelineItems.name: Frank Cobbina
timelineItems.text: Got a little worried there with Ayuk backflipping on a wet surface. But what a hit son, what a hit. #DOOP

timelineItems.name: The U Match Day
timelineItems.text: Ball falls to Ayuk in the box and he volleys it into the back of the net. Assist to C.J. Sapong for teeing it up for him #PHIvMTL

timelineItems.name: John Rossi
timelineItems.text: Is it too late to bring Sapong to the Gold Cup? #PHIvMTL

timelineItems.name: Phil Naegely
timelineItems.text: It’s rainy; It’s windy. But there is soccer to be played at PPL Park. #DOOP #PHIvMTL

timelineItems.name: Mike Standish
timelineItems.text: Watching #PHIvMTL is worth it just for the horrible Philly weather. It's a mud pit at PPL Park.

timelineItems.name: Dena Driscoll
timelineItems.text: #DOOP http://t.co/XdSiJt1HnV
